# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Released]
## [2.0.0] - 30-04-2023
### Added
- Now description is managed by a schema
- Support mongodb
- Management Account

### Changed
- Description migration to mongo

### Fixed
- If not found or other error in persistent launch one exception

## [1.1.0] - 04-02-2023
### Added
- Schema dynamic for definition description table

### Changed
- Table for the descriptions of video is Json dynamic (use with MongoDB)

## [1.0.1] - 23-12-2022
### Fixed
- When download manga of type 'list' convert to 'page'

## [1.0.0] - 17-12-2022
### Version Stable